title: What was the number one hit song in 1955? - Quora

response.answer_text: What genre? 1955 was the beginning of Dowop for white teens thanks to Alan Freed. Corina, Corina, Earth Angel, My Prayer. RockaBilly came in with Presley, Gene Vincent, Carl Perkins. Country came in with Western Swing, Lefty, Webb Pierce, Cash, Bakersfield Ca sound.
